{"tid":884540,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"而家有幾多人係會 先出後入？","createTime":"2018-10-31T16:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T18:19:03.000Z","uid":158245,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"969dfdd575242c67b21e3856e170d0e231f89d09","tid":884540,"uid":158245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"頭先搭地鐵返屋企，<br />\n到站果時己經見到有2條友係月台企正門口<br />\n開左門 佢地都冇意識擋住左人，要讓人落左車先<br />\n然後我行前左一步，企左係度唔郁（睇佢咩反應<br />\n點知個啊嬸格硬 打側行入車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後同行麻甩佬仲係咁啤住我<br />\n雖然冇法例係一定要比人出左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但正常禮儀啦<br />\n係d 廢老唔識 定 而家d人 都唔會讓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6b1b33987fbc4b6d4ea45693626452fd05ca52","tid":884540,"uid":48577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"先出未試過 但試過後入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d4068c474ac8ee506cbfe46c59d28014f736e1","tid":884540,"uid":54524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:30:41.000Z","msg":"出左仲入到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1333d9c806ff0323e65875694d936058f95041","tid":884540,"uid":63440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:36:27.000Z","msg":"見到咁既情況 一定大力撞出去<br />\n特別係見到出面一班大陸人同細佬"},{"pid":"3df0ab0205ee4a12e197407447898edfef0e45ac","tid":884540,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"好睇另一條隊條友讓唔讓先<br />\n同埋車廂多唔多人<br />\n如果車廂多人 隔離條隊又唔讓的話<br />\n我都唔會讓 因為讓左就冇位上"},{"pid":"c9c152827c6348ea0918bcaf03495c48046b1317","tid":884540,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"睇幾點，不過多數都關廢老內地人事"},{"pid":"974f21e82fd92b4f72f7f1a926bea37a2f8108f6","tid":884540,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"reply